				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="#">Automatic refresh for the ticket page</a>
					<p class="help-text">
						posted by laurence fishburne, 1 year ago <br />
						<a href="#">Last reply</a> by Sierra Daley 17 hours ago 
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="#">Create a ticket *without* an email address</a>
					<p class="help-text">
						posted by laurence fishburne, 1 year ago <br />
						<a href="#">Last reply</a> by Sierra Daley 17 hours ago 
					</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<a href="#" class="see-more">See all 10 topics</a>
		</section>
	</div>
</section>